          "audioUrl": "audio/astro_match_start_haze_astro_troubadour_convo03_01.mp3",
          "text": "I don't think I ever said thank you.",
          "duration": 2.348
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Haze",
          "audioFile": "haze_match_start_haze_astro_troubadour_convo03_02",
          "audioUrl": "audio/haze_match_start_haze_astro_troubadour_convo03_02.mp3",
          "text": "No need to thank me, we were both doing our job.",
          "duration": 3.673
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Holliday",
          "audioFile": "astro_match_start_haze_astro_troubadour_convo03_03",
          "audioUrl": "audio/astro_match_start_haze_astro_troubadour_convo03_03.mp3",
          "text": "We didn't just stop the troubadour, you kept me from crossing a line, and I owe you for that.",
          "duration": 6.291
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "character": "Haze",
          "audioFile": "haze_match_start_haze_astro_troubadour_convo03_04",
          "audioUrl": "audio/haze_match_start_haze_astro_troubadour_convo03_04.mp3",
          "text": "We can talk later, let's focus on the task at hand.",
          "duration": 3.579
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "calico_holliday_convo01",
